    <title>Massachusetts governor won’t sign facial recognition ban</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EcjhZVueXpOjD6WAIiHZH9E0cWI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/68525691/acastro_180730_1777_facial_recognition_0001.0.jpg" /&gt;
